      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> chicken breast strips</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-2-1681210882213-x200.jpg",
