            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced tomato</strong> and <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> in a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your<strong> ground sumac</strong> (save the rest for later!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Greek-style salad</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>naan[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-2-1681210942365-x200.jpg",
