      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Load up the <strong>warmed naan</strong> with the <strong>Greek-style salad</strong> and <strong>Mediterranean-style chicken</strong> – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style chicken gyros</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>tzatziki mayo</strong> and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> dressed shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
